_sText:
Well this is my 3rd map.
This is like a small saga so this is a return to the previous map that I made, making it alot bigger and alot better looking.
The azdu is aztec and dust into one, the theme follows this and so does the textures.
I tryed to create a map which has balance, so that zombies dont overrun it and also that people cannot camp in impossible places, which slows the game down.
There is a dedicated campers room, I hope they enjoy it.
Overall im pretty happy with it, I think it#s a big improvment over my last map, the next one will be even better.
I would have liked to have done alot more with the displacement but it leaks and becomes alot of work and I have spent alot of time on this already.

I hope you enjoy.
